{"tid":1793464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有時覺得，無論自己做咩d女都唔當自己一回事","createTime":"2019-12-22T12:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T13:13:43.000Z","uid":58316,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"93733f709f1f5eba86b2de285b3067dcc8e2d139","tid":1793464,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:06:59.000Z","msg":"就算有錢<br />\n有事業有成就<br />\n都係吼呢d<br />\n到自己一無所有<br />\n真係咩都唔係<br />\n不過又可以點<br />\n情願咁<br />\n情願d女真心睇自己唔起<br />\n好過扮野<br />\n情願嫌棄<br />\n情願不屑同自己講野<br />\n望一眼都好似非禮咁<br />\n好過千依百順<br />\n但心裏面恥笑你<br />\n其實我係知<br />\n眼神係睇得出<br />\nd女每次不經意輕佻笑一聲<br />\n自己個心就痛一下<br />\n其實所有野都看在眼裏<br />\n唯有自己行開<br />\n合埋眼<br />\n冷靜過後又再做人"},{"pid":"a423cb645db2be25c923d480be8907efb7dd2029","tid":1793464,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:07:10.000Z","msg":"【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【置頂】【行動po求推】好㷫呀！警曱向人群舉槍，聽日同我即刻行動。而嚟緊嘅行動係1223stuck稅局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793389</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvBryAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvBryAY.jpg&h=fea3e57a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddDxvuv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddDxvuv.jpg&h=525dd049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=3fb6504a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=0a097885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"102c5ca6a9f9b2cd76ebf92f0c013b61efdcf92f","tid":1793464,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，到我們的網站 <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctDwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=ee2ede04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"33bc945db274f712d4d9b6d1bced9114eb57f430","tid":1793464,"uid":225733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:13:43.000Z","msg":"不要看現實，不要看別人，不要看自己，因為這三件事也讓我傷心"}]}